<view class='index'>
    <view class='head whiteBg'>
        <view class='title'>{{list.title}}</view>
        <view class='info'>
            <image mode='aspectFill' src='{{list.headimgurl}}'></image>
            <text class='name'>{{list.createUserName}}</text>
            <text class='dateTime'>{{list.lastModifyDate}}</text>
            <text wx:if="{{list.category==1}}" class='type typeTag tagGreen'>公益活动</text>
            <text wx:elif="{{list.category==2}}" class='type typeTag tagPurPle'>普及活动</text>
            <text wx:elif="{{list.category==3}}" class='type typeTag tagYellow'>创意活动</text>
            <text wx:elif="{{list.category==4}}"  class='type typeTag tagRed'>党建活动</text>
        </view>
        <view class='bottom-line'></view>
    </view>
    <view class='body separate whiteBg'>
        <view class='content'>

            <block wx:for="{{list.content}}">

                <block wx:if="{{item.type==1}}">
                    <view>{{item.content}}</view>
                </block>
                <block wx:else>
                    <image mode="widthFix" src='{{item.content}}' />
                </block>
            </block>
        </view>
    </view>

    <view class='foot whiteBg'>
        <view class='comments'>
            <view class='comment bottom-line'>
                <view class='top'>
                    <image mode='aspectFill' src='http://pic.616pic.com/bg_w1180/00/05/65/Z5fAJclFBJ.jpg!/fw/1120'></image>


                    <view class='right'>
                        <view class='name'>半分</view>
                        <view class='time'>2018-04-03 13:15</view>
                    </view>
                </view>
                <view class='bottom '>
                    多杰出的创意品牌将在这里双双呈现罕见的创意合作，你还可以加入互动，亲手参与创作，相信你能从这些专心致志因此非常快乐的年轻人身上，找到属于你的乐趣。
                </view>
            </view>

            <view class='comment bottom-line'>
                <view class='top'>
                    <image mode='aspectFill' src='http://pic.616pic.com/bg_w1180/00/05/65/Z5fAJclFBJ.jpg!/fw/1120'></image>


                    <view class='right'>
                        <view class='name'>半分</view>
                        <view class='time'>2018-04-03 13:15</view>
                    </view>
                </view>
                <view class='bottom'>
                    多杰出的创意品牌将在这里双双呈现罕见的创意合作，你还可以加入互动，亲手参与创作，相信你能从这些专心致志因此非常快乐的年轻人身上，找到属于你的乐趣。
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>

    <view class='commentBox whiteBg top-line'>
        <view bindtap='actionComment' class='input'>一起参与讨论</view>
        <text class='iconfont icon-dianzan pop'> <text>2000</text> </text>
        <text class='iconfont icon-pinglun pop'> <text>2000</text></text>
    </view>
    <view class="model" wx:if='{{actionComment}}'>
        <view class='inner-model' catchtap='hiddenComment'></view>
        <view class='box whiteBg'>
            <form bindsubmit="formSubmit" bindreset="formReset">
                <textarea bindinput='getValue' focus="true" auto-focus='true' cursor-spacing='80' auto-height='true' adjust-position='false' show-confirm-bar=''></textarea>
                <button class='submit' formType="submit">发送</button>
            </form>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>